title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 17 2022
itunes:title: Clay Travis and Buck Sexton Show H2 – Jun 17 2022
description:
Biden's gas rebate card nixed by chip shortage. Mayra Flores calls VP Harris "useless," comments on Elon Musk's support. Granholm on alternative energy. Carl Bernstein claims Jan. 6 was worse than the Civil War. Georgia Governor Brian Kemp joins C&B to discuss the World Cup in Atlanta and beating Stacey Abrams. Senate gun bill might fall apart, Biden leaves for beach house. C&B take calls.

Follow Clay & Buck on YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/clayandbuck
